{
  "stem": "3212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a train that you didn't have a seat where to sit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had all to stand or sit on the suitcases.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Boxcars.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the cars were not open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had a roof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it had a roof, it had little windows with bars on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this boxcar, I-- I-- if I can remember, it was about 70 or 80 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was loaded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was full.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember how we urinated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember what we did for a toilet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know only it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing to drink.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had only food what we took with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What I never will forget is we had some jewelry at home, and what we brought to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had a handbag.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And before we left our home-- our apartment in Vienna-- my mother put everything in a cooking top and put over it-- she first made [NON-ENGLISH] they call it in Austria.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She took [GERMAN]-- flour and oil, and cooked it and put it over that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in this handbag, we had all our jewelry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This we took with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This we could-- they didn't-- we couldn't take furniture, but suitcases or handbags we could take.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And whatever food we had, we took.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had to eat on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The memories of Vienna-- Vienna-- as a child, I remember it was a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember they had a [GERMAN], what they call it here, like a little Disneyland, that you could see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was forest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was movies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was all kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were many things we couldn't go into it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But Vienna, as I remember, it was a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
